               <code codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" code="34069-5" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Chlorzoxazone tablets, USP are available as oblong, scored, white tablets debossed with WPI on one side and "39"-"68" on the other side and are packaged in bottles of 7, 30, 40, 60 and 90.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Store at 20° to 25°C (68° to 77°F) [See USP Controlled Room Temperature].</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Dispense contents with a child-resistant closure (as required) and in a tight container as defined in the USP/NF.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Keep out of the reach of children.</content>
                  </paragraph>
